{"tid":1211151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當香港人被順服 中共就真的贏了","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T17:16:36.000Z","uid":168169,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d360acd3ac3d4e474d6a423734f4b5f319835c15","tid":1211151,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"憤怒 但請別忘記反抗<br />\n<br />\n100萬人上街 政府無視人民訴求<br />\n到咗 9 12，武力鎮壓完再將責任推晒落市民身上<br />\n就算就算政府聼日撤回方案，佢想俾出個訊息就係香港人反抗係無用<br />\n如果將呢種無力化植入曬落香港人身上，諗兩諗就放棄反抗，最後香港人就同一般大陸人無分別<br />\n所以香港人切記千萬不要被順服<br />\n<br />\n電影《星際啟示錄》Interstellar 有段詩句好啱用<br />\n<br />\nDo not go gentle into that good night, ／不要坐以待夜<br />\nOld age should burn and rave at close of day ／白晝將盡，晚年應在遲暮時燃燒與咆哮；<br />\nRage, rage against the dying of the light. ／憤怒，憤怒地抗拒光明的消逝。<br />\nThough wise men at their end know dark is right, ／縱是智者自知黑暗合乎倫常，<br />\nBecause their words had forked no lightning they ／因他們的語言未曾發光發亮，他們<br />\nDo not go gentle into that good night.／不要坐以待夜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論今晚決定留守，抑或用其他方式抗爭既市民，<br />\n或者大家有唔同諗法同抗爭方式<br />\n但都千其唔好忘記我地既憤怒，不要被順服"},{"pid":"a7e6b71af027a00995944a76b35c05d5c9b2a43a","tid":1211151,"uid":168169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f072b2b218397e721cafc6e7fb7d9a2c8444dd","tid":1211151,"uid":200432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"我都有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14382d7b3193a4b3162ff83fc799c4767162a67f","tid":1211151,"uid":168169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c8eb942e0955a2866069c017a80e0c63ab63b6c","tid":1211151,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb991bcb28395f2d480d3e32421b7b886bc3a8ac","tid":1211151,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0